\"Create a text-light Rath Yatra chariot craft sheet image with simple shapes and blank labels, no deity likenesses.\"},{\"body\":\"Explain this warranty in plain English. I’ll upload a photo or paste the key lines. Point out questions to ask, without giving legal advice.\",\"title\":\"Explain a warranty clearly\"},{\"body\":\"Create a folder system for my digital files. Ask what I mostly store, then suggest folder names and simple rules.\",\"title\":\"Tidy your digital files\"},{\"body\":\"Create a calm, text-light visual card for a 20-minute reading routine, with simple step icons and space for handwritten notes.\",\"title\":\"Make a reading routine card\"},{\"body\":\"Help me make a CUET college preference shortlist. Ask my course first, then create a comparison table I can fill.\",\"title\":\"Build a CUET shortlist\"},{\"title\":\"Decode Wimbledon scoring\",\"body\":\"Teach me Wimbledon scoring like I’m watching for the first time, with a playful mini quiz at the end.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a cosy, text-light image of an Indian monsoon snack platter for home inspiration. No brand names or readable labels.\",\"title\":\"Sketch a rainy snack platter\"},{\"body\":\"Help me make a spoiler-free OTT watchlist from current India releases. Ask my preferred language or mood, then suggest what to try first.\",\"title\":\"Build a spoiler-free watchlist\"},{\"title\":\"Make a snack tasting sheet\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light monsoon snack tasting sheet with five blank slots, simple spice and crunch icons, and no brand names.\"},{\"body\":\"Show me a 15-second Reel structure for teaching one small idea. Ask me for the topic first, then make a shot-by-shot plan.\",\"title\":\"Practise a 15-second Reel\"},{\"title\":\"Improve a board answer\",\"body\":\"I’ll paste a board-style answer. Improve it for marks, keep my points, and show a 3-line examiner-friendly version.\"},{\"title\":\"Check if a FASTag pass helps\",\"body\":\"Help me decide if the FASTag Annual Pass is worth checking. Ask my vehicle type and usual highway trips, then compare fit, not exact savings.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a calmer travel day\",\"body\":\"Help me make a travel-day plan with buffer time, snacks and document checks. Ask the journey type first.\"},{\"body\":\"Make my next 5 tiffins feel less repetitive. Ask me for a kitchen photo or ingredient list, then suggest easy mix-and-match ideas.\",\"title\":\"Plan a no-bore tiffin week\"},{\"body\":\"Help me reset a messy desk or room. Ask for a photo or short description, then give me a 20-minute plan.\",\"title\":\"Reset a messy space\"},{\"body\":\"Plan 5 simple tiffin ideas using Indian home staples. Ask who it is for and any food restrictions before making the plan.\",\"title\":\"Plan a no-fuss tiffin week\"},{\"title\":\"Plan around a waitlisted ticket\",\"body\":\"My train ticket is WL or RAC. Explain what it means and help me plan a backup without guessing confirmation chances.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me prepare for a difficult conversation. Ask who it is with, then draft a calm opening and likely replies.\",\"title\":\"Prepare a hard conversation\"},{\"body\":\"Make a monsoon train carry-on list for my route. Ask destination and train class first, then keep it one-bag friendly.\",\"title\":\"Pack for a monsoon train\"},{\"title\":\"Make a chariot explainer\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light Rath Yatra learning graphic with three simple chariots, symbol icons and blank labels. No faces or logos.\"},{\"title\":\"Plan a monsoon snack\",\"body\":\"I want a rainy-day snack at home. I can upload a kitchen photo or list 3 ingredients. Suggest one quick option and a chai pairing.\"},{\"body\":\"Help me pick a fun neutral team to follow at the FIFA World Cup. Ask one question first, then give a playful shortlist.\",\"title\":\"Pick my World Cup side quest\"},{\"title\":\"Get into Wimbledon\",\"body\":\"Give me a beginner-friendly Wimbledon 2026 guide for watching from India. Explain the format, terms and matches to follow.\"},{\"body\":\"Create a simple concept map for a topic I’m studying. Ask me the topic first, then keep the image text-light.\",\"title\":\"Draw a concept map\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light notice graphic for an apartment water or power issue. Use blank space for timing and contact details outside the image.\",\"title\":\"Make a simple society notice\"},{\"title\":\"Choose monsoon-friendly fabric\",\"body\":\"Teach me how to choose monsoon-friendly fabrics and footwear for daily wear, without assuming my budget or city.\"},{\"title\":\"Try a regional film night\",\"body\":\"Find a current Indian regional trailer that suits a light film night, then suggest a no-spoiler watch plan.\"},{\"body\":\"Draft a polite apartment-society notice for a water cut. Ask me the date and duration first, then write group-message and notice-board versions.\",\"title\":\"Draft a society notice\"},{\"title\":\"Make a tiffin idea wheel\",\"body\":\"Create a text-light tiffin idea wheel with simple food icons and blank labels. Ask my main flavour preference first.\"},{\"title\":\"Prep for Passport Seva\",\"body\":\"Help me prepare for a Passport Seva appointment. Ask which service it is, then make an official-doc checklist and visit-day plan.\"},{\"title\":\"Draw your budget buckets\",\"body\":\"Create a simple budget bucket diagram with generic icons and three blank labels. Keep any written guidance outside the image.\"},{\"body\":\"Use a recent India ODI scorecard to teach me how a chase is paced: powerplay, middle overs, required run rate and wickets.\",\"title\":\"Understand an ODI chase\"},{\"title\":\"Sort ITR papers before filing\",\"body\":\"Help me make an ITR document folder for AY 2026-27. Ask only my income type first, then list likely documents to collect.\"},{\"title\":\"Sort my paperwork pile\",\"body\":\"Help me sort a pile of bills, forms and notes. Ask what categories I see, then give me a quick filing plan.\"},{\"title\":\"Explain the 48-team chaos\",\"body\":\"Explain the 48-team World Cup format like I’m joining a group chat late, with a tiny glossary and a playful example.\"},{\"title\":\"Learn women’s T20 terms\",\"body\":\"Explain five T20 cricket terms I’ll hear during India Women’s matches, with examples from the current World Cup.\"},{\"body\":\"Find a current Indian music trend for a short video idea. Ask what the video is about, then suggest a clean hook and caption.\",\"title\":\"Choose a Reel soundtrack\"},{\"body\":\"Create a text-light doodle showing when to use cash, UPI Lite or normal UPI. Check current rules first.\",\"title\":\"Draw a UPI payment flow\"}]},\"is_device_based\":true,\"passed\":true},\"3165814200\":{\"name\":\"3165814200\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"JITTER_MAXIMUM\":1,\"MIN_RETRY_INTERVAL\":300,\"MAX_RETRY_INTERVAL\":5000,\"RETRY_FACTOR\":1.5,\"MAX_RETRY_COUNT\":12,\"JITTER_MINIMUM\":0.5},\"is_device_based\":false,\"passed\":false},\"1171720776\":{\"name\":\"1171720776\",\"rule_id\":\"1UlyxkYHQbchoVfpaOhLvD\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"stableID\",\"value\":{\"enabled\":true},\"is_device_based\":true,\"group_name\":\"Control\",\"is_experiment_active\":true,\"is_user_in_experiment\":true},\"3635154224\":{\"name\":\"3635154224\",\"rule_id\":\"default\",\"secondary_exposures\":[],\"id_type\":\"userID\",\"value\":{\"connector_to_read_scopes\":{\"connector_openai_medical_records\":[\"HEALTH\"],\"connector_openai_olympic\":[\"HEALTH\"],\"connector_2b0a9009c9c64bf9933a3dae3f2b1254\":[\"HEALTH\"]},\"connector_to_allowed_with_approval_scopes\":{\"connector_openai_olympic\":[\"HEALTH\"],\"asdk_app_6945d9d84c5c8191a28343ae9d7b6e8b\":[\"HEALTH\"],\"asdk_app_6949b36d7c008191b61e56d4ada8cff2\":[\"HEALTH\"],\"connector_68f1afc5a6008191a701eaaab428816c\":[\"HEALTH\"],\"connector_openai_deep_research\":[\"HEALTH\"],\"connector_68f1abff1b688191b9309a31c9b4a713\":[\"HEALTH\"],\"connector_2b0a9009c9c64bf9933a3dae3f2b1254\":[\"HEALTH\"],\"connecto